@page "/overlays"

<PageTitle>模态框与侧边栏 (Modals & Offcanvas) - Bootstrap 展示</PageTitle>

<h2>🪟 模态框与侧边栏 (Modals & Offcanvas)</h2>
<p class="lead">用于提示/确认的模态对话框 (Modal) 以及侧边面板 (Offcanvas)。</p>

<h5 class="mt-4">模态框示例 (Modal Examples)</h5>
<div class="border rounded p-4 bg-light mb-4 d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#demoModal">
        基础模态框
    </button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#staticModal">
        静态遮罩 (Static Backdrop)
    </button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-info text-white" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#scrollModal">
        可滚动模态框
    </button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-success" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#centeredModal">
        垂直居中
    </button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#smallModal">
        小尺寸 (sm)
    </button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-warning" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#largeModal">
        大尺寸 (lg)
    </button>
</div>

<!-- 基础模态框 -->
<div class="modal fade" id="demoModal" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h5 class="modal-title">模态框标题</h5>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <p>这是一个基础 Bootstrap 模态对话框。点击外部区域或 X 按钮即可关闭。</p>
                <p>模态框由 HTML、CSS 和 JS 构建。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">关闭 (Close)</button>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">保存更改</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- 静态遮罩模态框 -->
<div class="modal fade" id="staticModal" data-bs-backdrop="static" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h5 class="modal-title">静态遮罩</h5>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <p>🔒 点击外部区域不会关闭此模态框。必须使用按钮来关闭。</p>
                <p>使用 <code>data-bs-backdrop="static"</code> 属性。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger" data-bs-dismiss="modal">我知道了</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- 可滚动模态框 -->
<div class="modal fade" id="scrollModal" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header"><h5 class="modal-title">可滚动内容</h5><button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button></div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                @for (int i = 1; i <= 10; i++)
                {
                    <p>第 @i 行：这是一些用于展示模态框内部滚动行为的占位内容。长内容会导致模态框主体区域出现滚动条。</p>
                }
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer"><button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">关闭</button></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- 垂直居中模态框 -->
<div class="modal fade" id="centeredModal" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header"><h5 class="modal-title">垂直居中</h5><button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button></div>
            <div class="modal-body"><p>此模态框使用 <code>.modal-dialog-centered</code> 实现垂直居中。</p></div>
            <div class="modal-footer"><button type="button" class="btn btn-success" data-bs-dismiss="modal">知道了！</button></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- 小尺寸模态框 -->
<div class="modal fade" id="smallModal" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-sm">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header"><h5 class="modal-title">小尺寸模态框</h5><button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button></div>
            <div class="modal-body"><p>使用 <code>.modal-sm</code> 的小尺寸模态框。</p></div>
            <div class="modal-footer"><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" data-bs-dismiss="modal">确定</button></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- 大尺寸模态框 -->
<div class="modal fade" id="largeModal" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header"><h5 class="modal-title">大尺寸模态框</h5><button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button></div>
            <div class="modal-body"><p>使用 <code>.modal-lg</code> 的大尺寸模态框，适合更复杂的内容。</p></div>
            <div class="modal-footer"><button type="button" class="btn btn-warning" data-bs-dismiss="modal">关闭</button></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<h5 class="mt-4">侧边面板 (Offcanvas)</h5>
<div class="border rounded p-4 bg-light mb-4 d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
    <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" data-bs-toggle="offcanvas" data-bs-target="#offcanvasStart">左侧弹出 (start)</button>
    <button class="btn btn-success" type="button" data-bs-toggle="offcanvas" data-bs-target="#offcanvasEnd">右侧弹出 (end)</button>
    <button class="btn btn-warning" type="button" data-bs-toggle="offcanvas" data-bs-target="#offcanvasTop">顶部弹出 (top)</button>
    <button class="btn btn-danger" type="button" data-bs-toggle="offcanvas" data-bs-target="#offcanvasBottom">底部弹出 (bottom)</button>
    <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary" type="button" data-bs-toggle="offcanvas" data-bs-target="#offcanvasBackdrop" data-bs-backdrop="static">静态遮罩</button>
</div>

<!-- 左侧 Offcanvas -->
<div class="offcanvas offcanvas-start" tabindex="-1" id="offcanvasStart">
    <div class="offcanvas-header">
        <h5 class="offcanvas-title">左侧侧边栏</h5>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="offcanvas"></button>
    </div>
    <div class="offcanvas-body">
        <p>左侧侧边面板的内容。从左侧滑入。</p>
        <hr>
        <p>使用 <code>.offcanvas-start</code> 实现左侧弹出。</p>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- 右侧 Offcanvas -->
<div class="offcanvas offcanvas-end" tabindex="-1" id="offcanvasEnd">
    <div class="offcanvas-header">
        <h5 class="offcanvas-title">右侧侧边栏</h5>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="offcanvas"></button>
    </div>
    <div class="offcanvas-body">
        <p>从右侧滑入。使用 <code>.offcanvas-end</code>。</p>
        <div class="mb-3">
            <label class="form-label">侧边栏中的表单示例：</label>
            <input class="form-control" placeholder="输入内容...">
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- 顶部 Offcanvas -->
<div class="offcanvas offcanvas-top" tabindex="-1" id="offcanvasTop" style="height:35vh">
    <div class="offcanvas-header">
        <h5 class="offcanvas-title">顶部侧边栏</h5>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="offcanvas"></button>
    </div>
    <div class="offcanvas-body"><p>从顶部向下滑入。使用 <code>.offcanvas-top</code>。</p></div>
</div>

<!-- 底部 Offcanvas -->
<div class="offcanvas offcanvas-bottom" tabindex="-1" id="offcanvasBottom" style="height:35vh">
    <div class="offcanvas-header">
        <h5 class="offcanvas-title">底部侧边栏</h5>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="offcanvas"></button>
    </div>
    <div class="offcanvas-body"><p>从底部向上滑入。使用 <code>.offcanvas-bottom</code>。</p></div>
</div>

<!-- 静态遮罩 Offcanvas -->
<div class="offcanvas offcanvas-end" tabindex="-1" id="offcanvasBackdrop" data-bs-backdrop="static">
    <div class="offcanvas-header">
        <h5 class="offcanvas-title">静态遮罩</h5>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="offcanvas"></button>
    </div>
    <div class="offcanvas-body">
        <p>🔒 点击外部区域无法关闭此面板。必须使用关闭按钮。</p>
    </div>
</div>
